  "detailed_description": "The time has come to bring justice upon those treacherous vampires. Embark on a golf-like journey in this short game with golf controls. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566150/extras/43d3db06e8d861b0c4b9f165ca849dc4.poster.avif?t=1695963701\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566150/extras/43d3db06e8d861b0c4b9f165ca849dc4.webm?t=1695963701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566150/extras/43d3db06e8d861b0c4b9f165ca849dc4.mp4?t=1695963701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Hunt some vampires by controlling your character like a golf-ball. Learn the hard truth about being a vampire slayer.<br></li><li> Spend collected money to upgrade your character between levels<br></li><li> Custom game mode with two types of levels: maze that needs to be completed and open-world where you can move freely</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566150/extras/204ad815b77f5bab0f78d4c20da19bdc.poster.avif?t=1695963701\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566150/extras/204ad815b77f5bab0f78d4c20da19bdc.webm?t=1695963701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566150/extras/204ad815b77f5bab0f78d4c20da19bdc.mp4?t=1695963701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
